    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "3n1VF",
      "x": 3900,
      "y": 2920,
      "name": "Spec: Sheet Sizing",
      "width": 280,
      "height": 160,
      "content": "Bottom Sheet Behavior\n\n• Initial height: min(content, 72svh)\n• Max height: 90svh\n• Header stays visible\n• Rules list + add section scroll as one content area"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "2W8pc",
      "x": 4189,
      "y": 2920,
      "name": "Spec: Dismiss",
      "width": 280,
      "height": 140,
      "content": "Dismiss Behavior\n\n• Close button, swipe down, tap scrim all dismiss\n• If form has unsaved input, dismiss allowed (no confirm)\n• Background page scroll locked while sheet is open"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "PDT4u",
      "x": 3900,
      "y": 3164,
      "name": "Spec: Keyboard",
      "width": 280,
      "height": 110,
      "content": "Keyboard Behavior\n\n• On input focus, sheet expands toward max height\n• Scroll content so focused input + Add Rule button remain visible above keyboard"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "oC1Nu",
      "x": 4189,
      "y": 3164,
      "name": "Spec: Rule State Model",
      "width": 280,
      "height": 251,
      "content": "Rule State Model\n\n• enabled (boolean): user toggle via kebab menu\n• effective_state (computed): active | filtered_out | clamped | no_match | disabled\n• If enabled=false → badge shows 'disabled' regardless"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "Lk9Xz",
      "x": 3900,
      "y": 3396,
      "name": "Spec: List Loading Strategy",
      "width": 280,
      "height": 210,
      "content": "List Loading Strategy\n\n• NOT infinite scroll — uses cursor-based load-more pagination\n• Footer shows 'Showing N–M of total' + 'Load more ↓' button\n• Impl: cursor-based fetch + DOM virtualization / windowing\n• Keeps continuous browse feel with bounded memory footprint"
    },
